Before heading to the solution let us see all possible form of testcases for the given question.

1. Maximum path exist in the left-subtree or right-subtree. shown in example (i) & (ii).
1. Maximum path is the sum of the part of left-subtree , right-subtree and root. shown in example (iii).
1. Maximum path is the sum of the (Maximum consecutive path of left-subtree and right-subtree) and root. shown in example (iv) & (v).

![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/452ee832-327d-4443-aae0-699148a7a4ef_1685568434.8347857.png)

